---
// Full-bleed photo with a single guest quote overlay — a scroll-rhythm
// interrupt between the Picker (bone) and ExploreCards (bone). Per CRO
// research: image-led pattern interrupts mid-page lift conversion by
// ~19% on long pages by grabbing attention from scroll-skippers.
// Photo: Dodie's real on-deck view of the BVI headlands from the side
// deck of the catamaran — bimini overhead, white deck and winches in
// the foreground, deep blue water and green islands stretching to the
// horizon. Matches the Emily quote's BVI voyage context.
---

<section class="relative bg-primary text-ink overflow-hidden">
  <img
    src="/img/source/destinations/bvi-deck-view-headlands.jpg"
    alt="View from the side deck of the catamaran across deep blue water to the green headlands of the British Virgin Islands"
    loading="lazy"
    decoding="async"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
  />
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/85 via-primary/40 to-primary/20"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-7 lg:px-14 py-32 lg:py-44 min-h-[60dvh] flex flex-col justify-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[0.625rem] font-semibold text-sun mb-8">
        From the logbook · BVI · 2025
      </p>
      <blockquote
        class="font-serif-quote italic text-ink leading-[1.3] tracking-[-0.015em] text-balance"
        style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw + 1rem, 2.5rem); font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 72, 'SOFT' 60, 'WONK' 1;"
      >
        <span class="text-sun text-[3rem] leading-none -ml-2 mr-1 align-middle" aria-hidden="true" style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144;">&ldquo;</span>Eight days and I never once checked my email. Closest thing to a reset button I've ever paid for.
      </blockquote>
      <p class="mt-8 font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[0.625rem] font-semibold text-ink/85">
        Emily R. · Portland, OR · British Virgin Islands voyage
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <a
          href="/calendar"
          class="group inline-flex items-center gap-3 font-label-caps uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-ink border-b-2 border-sun pb-1 hover:text-sun transition-colors"
        >
          See the weeks Emily booked
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="size-3 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M1 8h13M9 3l5 5-5 5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
